{"tid":2346194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中槍男坐輪椅出庭 索警武力指引","createTime":"2020-12-30T05:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:02:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cc8fee0acf7286deb4b7b329ad91991469b4e8","tid":2346194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/MQITLNMECRDTDMC44BT5PIEDFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FMQITLNMECRDTDMC44BT5PIEDFY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=97191a0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FMQITLNMECRDTDMC44BT5PIEDFY%2F&h=456a76d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/MQITLNMECRDTDMC44BT5PIEDFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中槍男坐輪椅出庭 索警武力指引<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_94vbzLIvkIeSpOtrpoWBk3-85U=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6YH43F2XPRHPVB2F4UTZFQVXQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_94vbzLIvkIeSpOtrpoWBk3-85U%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6YH43F2XPRHPVB2F4UTZFQVXQA.jpg&h=acedf3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告周柏均被控搶槍及阻差等罪，昨坐輪椅出庭。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月在西灣河被交通警連開三槍，近距離擊中腹部的21歲學生「熊仔餅」周柏均，與其同伴事後被控企圖搶槍及阻差辦公等罪，案件昨於區域法院提訊。辯方庭上稱，已向控方提出要求披露包括警方使用武力的指引等文件，控方則以文件受公眾利益豁免權保護，需時考慮，建議法庭可先定審期。法官考慮後，將案件押後至明年3月23日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n術後胃腸劇痛屢入院<br />\n<br />\n周柏均昨坐輪椅到庭。他透露，上次手術後出現腸黏連的後遺症，每日忍受胃痛和腸痛，尤以月底發作最嚴重，更不能飲食。周曾有兩三次因為疼痛嚴重而入院，「嘔晒食嘅嘢，黃膽水都嘔埋，所以咁瘦」。<br />\n<br />\n周柏均（21歲）及胡子鍵（20歲）共被控。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年周中槍後送院搶救；他右腹中槍，傷及肝臟和腎臟，子彈卡在背脊，需切除右腎及部份肝臟。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC475/20"},{"pid":"289cddaa52eaf877eecb81c612f6cdebb09401a2","tid":2346194,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"武力指引：警務人員使用武力時以「往死裡打」為基本原則"}]}